column2: select Sum(Track.UnitPrice) as AlbumCost, Album.Title from chinook.Track inner join chinook.Album on chinook.Track.AlbumId=chinook.Album.AlbumId inner join chinook.Artist on chinook.Album.ArtistId=chinook.Artist.ArtistId group by Track.UnitPrice, Album.Title order by Track.UnitPrice desc limit #
